```plantuml
@startuml dspace-group_simphera-reference-architecture-azure
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "Administrator" as Admin

package "Azure" {
  rectangle "Azure Kubernetes Service\n(AKS)" as AKS #lightblue
  rectangle "Azure Database for\nPostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL #lightgreen
  rectangle "Azure Storage Accounts\n(MinIO)" as MinIO #lightyellow
  rectangle "Azure Key Vault" as KeyVault #lightpink
  rectangle "Virtual Network" as VNet #lightgray
  rectangle "Private Link" as PrivateLink #lightcoral
  rectangle "Windows VM\n(License Server)" as LicenseServer #lightpurple
  rectangle "Azure Log Analytics" as LogAnalytics #lightsteelblue
  rectangle "Bastion Host" as Bastion #lightgoldenrodyellow
}

Admin --> AKS : Deploy/Manage
Admin --> PostgreSQL : Configure
Admin --> MinIO : Access
Admin --> KeyVault : Manage Secrets
Admin --> VNet : Configure Networking
Admin --> LicenseServer : Manage License
Admin --> LogAnalytics : Monitor Logs
Admin --> Bastion : Secure Access

AKS --> PostgreSQL : Store Data
AKS --> MinIO : Use Storage
AKS --> KeyVault : Retrieve Secrets
AKS --> PrivateLink : Secure Connection

PostgreSQL --> PrivateLink : Secure Connection
MinIO --> PrivateLink : Secure Connection

VNet --> AKS
VNet --> PostgreSQL
VNet --> MinIO
VNet --> LicenseServer
VNet --> Bastion

@enduml
